sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Runner
    participant Ext as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RHReg as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AccReg as registry.access.redhat.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline
    participant Quay as quay.io/rhoai<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DC as Data Container<br/>(UBI9-minimal)
    participant Dash as RHOAI Dashboard

    Note over CI,Dash: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation (CI/CD)

    CI->>FS: Read models-index.yaml,<br/>validated-models-index.yaml,<br/>other-models-index.yaml
    CI->>Ext: Execute model-extractor
    Ext->>FS: Parse index YAML files
    FS-->>Ext: Model definitions

    par Fetch OCI Metadata
        Ext->>RHReg: GET /v2/.../manifests<br/>OCI Registry API v2
        RHReg-->>Ext: Image manifests,<br/>architectures, timestamps
    and Fetch HuggingFace Metadata
        Ext->>HF: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN (optional)
        HF-->>Ext: Model details, README,<br/>collections, validation status
    end

    Note over Ext: Multi-source metadata merge<br/>7 priority levels with<br/>provenance tracking

    Ext->>FS: Write output/ (per-model YAML)
    Ext->>FS: Write data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>data/validated-models-catalog.yaml<br/>data/other-models-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,Dash: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation (CI/CD)

    CI->>Ext: Execute with -mcp-index flag
    Ext->>FS: Read *-mcp-servers-index.yaml
    Ext->>FS: Read input/mcp_servers/*.yaml
    Ext->>AccReg: GET /v2/.../manifests<br/>OCI Registry API v2
    AccReg-->>Ext: MCP server image metadata
    Ext->>FS: Write data/*-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,Dash: Flow 3: Container Build & Push

    Konflux->>FS: Dockerfile.konflux<br/>COPY data/*.yaml
    Konflux->>Quay: Push container image<br/>Auth: Quay credentials<br/>Multi-arch: x86_64, ppc64le,<br/>s390x, arm64

    Note over CI,Dash: Flow 4: Runtime Data Consumption (On-Cluster)

    DC->>DC: sleep infinity<br/>(data-only container)
    Dash->>DC: Volume mount /app/data
    DC-->>Dash: Catalog YAML files<br/>(shared filesystem)
